---
// This component demonstrates the agency crisis VastSilicon solves
---

<section id="agency-crisis" class="section-padding bg-gray-50" aria-labelledby="crisis-heading">
  <div class="container-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 id="crisis-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          The Agency Crisis
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Modern systems generate more choices, data, and nuance than humans can process. 
          This creates a critical gap between what's available to know and what's practical to act on.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Problem Demonstrations -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <!-- Problem: Food Choices -->
        <div class="problem-solution-card relative">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Overwhelmed in Grocery Aisles</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                45,000 products in an average supermarket. Misleading health claims. 
                Ingredients you can't pronounce. No time to research every choice.
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-red-700 bg-red-50 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg">
                Result: Decision paralysis or blind trust in marketing
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Solution: ChoiceCheck -->
        <div class="problem-solution-card solution relative">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Instant Clarity with ChoiceCheck</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Snap a photo. Get a clear 0-100 score. Understand exactly why. 
                Personalized to YOUR health goals and dietary needs.
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-green-700 bg-green-50 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg">
                Result: Confident decisions aligned with your values
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Problem: Financial Confusion -->
        <div class="problem-solution-card relative">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Money Mystery</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Where did my money go? Who owes what? Scattered transactions across cards, 
                apps, and cash. No clear picture of spending patterns.
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-red-700 bg-red-50 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg">
                Result: Financial stress and poor money decisions
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Solution: MoneyTide -->
        <div class="problem-solution-card solution relative">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Crystal Clear with MoneyTide</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Visual dashboards. Smart categorization. Fair expense splitting. 
                See exactly where your money flows and who owes what.
              </p>
              <div class="text-sm text-green-700 bg-green-50 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg">
                Result: Financial confidence and control
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- The Pattern -->
      <div class="text-center bg-white rounded-lg shadow-medium p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">The Pattern</h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Every domain where complexity has overwhelmed human choice follows the same pattern:
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-sm">
          <div class="bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <div class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">1. Complexity Explosion</div>
            <div class="text-red-700">Too many options, too much data, too little time</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-2">2. Agency Surrender</div>
            <div class="text-yellow-700">People default to whatever's easiest or most marketed</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <div class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">3. VastSilicon Solution</div>
            <div class="text-green-700">Translate complexity into clarity, preserve choice</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>